{"tid":373053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小巴上偷拍28歲女 休班警被捕","createTime":"2017-08-24T17:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T18:00:14.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2a72cec51d2a0be143b161b26388bd72e54b6e","tid":373053,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:27:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>小巴上偷拍28歲女 休班警被捕</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發  2017-08-25 00:30:28 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n昨凌晨零時許，一名姓張42歲休班警員，在旺角一輛小巴上懷疑偷拍一名28歲女子。警方接報到場，休班警涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢被捕，已獲准保釋候查，須於九月下旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e3e2075225e6e01e23512f989299132c39126c","tid":373053,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ba8b36139c2ccfd35d1ce87d0198ccb301d7b7","tid":373053,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:54:47.000Z","msg":"辣殺"},{"pid":"22937df84a4b1591c43520082c2332dfd05c256b","tid":373053,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"休班警加一分"},{"pid":"c88252efe2caf660abc9472d2c1244049fee165d","tid":373053,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:58:52.000Z","msg":"警隊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非常重視</span></span>人員的操守<br />\n<br />\n有事先講非常重佢地操守...請人前品格審查又唔做得嚴謹啲"},{"pid":"96da003db436ce295fe2f2af87ed00c0ce0dca24","tid":373053,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T18:00:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警隊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非常重視</span></span>人員的操守<br />\n<br />\n有事先講非常重佢地操守...請人前品格審查又唔做得嚴謹啲</blockquote><br />\n次次都係咁講架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}